data.text:
Skandinavisk Skog Hand Wash Boreal forests cover over half the Scandinavian lands, stretching from the southernmost county of Sweden to the Arctic Circle.

This moisturising hand wash is made in Denmark with 99% ingredients of natural origin, including 36% certified organic and 54% local spring water, plus 1% of their own fragrance. 450ml

Scent notes: Pine needles and fir cones, birch sap and woodland lily of the valley.
